====================================
1. Prerequisites
====================================
------------------
1.1 Dependencies
------------------
a. OpenCV 2.1 for VS2008
b. Microsoft TR1 extensions for VS2008

a. http://opencv.willowgarage.com/wiki/VisualC%2B%2B_VS2008
b. http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/en/confirmation.aspx?FamilyId=D466226B-8DAB-445F-A7B4-448B326C48E7&displaylang=en
b. http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/bb982198(v=VS.90).aspx

====================================
2. Usage
====================================
Generate Training Set for Training a Random Forest.
This part is without GPU acceleration.

